<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Couchbase on MCP Toolbox for Databases</title><link>https://mcp-toolbox.dev/dev/integrations/couchbase/</link><description>Recent content in Couchbase on MCP Toolbox for Databases</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://mcp-toolbox.dev/dev/integrations/couchbase/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Couchbase Source</title><link>https://mcp-toolbox.dev/dev/integrations/couchbase/source/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mcp-toolbox.dev/dev/integrations/couchbase/source/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="about"&gt;About&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;couchbase&lt;/code&gt; source establishes a connection to a Couchbase database cluster,
allowing tools to execute SQL queries against it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="available-tools"&gt;Available Tools&lt;/h2&gt;








 
 
 
 
 







 &lt;h3&gt;Couchbase Source Tools&lt;/h3&gt;
 
 &lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Tool Name&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="https://mcp-toolbox.dev/dev/integrations/couchbase/tools/couchbase-sql/"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;couchbase-sql&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;A &amp;#34;couchbase-sql&amp;#34; tool executes a pre-defined SQL statement against a Couchbase database.
&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
 &lt;/table&gt;









&lt;h2 id="example"&gt;Example&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;source&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;my-couchbase-instance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;couchbase&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;connectionString&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;couchbase://localhost&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;bucket&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;travel-sample&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;scope&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;inventory&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;username&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;Administrator&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;password&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;password&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="notice note" &gt;
